snippet.title: Betrayed: Official Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Get your friends and enemies ready to pick your battleground and weapons to fight the age-old fight: Good vs. Evil. Traitor vs. Innocent.

With new features, new maps, new everything! Play with up to 16 people, customize your character and game settings, and get ready to fight till the end.

Betrayed coming soon on Steam
Wishlist today! store.steampowered.com/app/2873490/Betrayed/
